1¤Rules for using your Dankort
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
These rules apply to the use of your Dankort. Unless otherwise
stated, these rules apply to the use as physical card and Dankort card
on mobile phone. The words and expressions used here are explained
at the end of this document.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2¤What can you use Dankort card for?
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
2.1¤Cash withdrawal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can use your Dankort card to withdraw cash from Danish cash
dispensers. You can also use your Dankort card to withdraw cash from
your own bank and most other Danish banks.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Charges in connection with the use of the card are stated in the
You may only withdraw cash or make purchases for the balance on your
account, unless you have a different agreement with &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Contactless function or Dankort card on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
When using non-contact payment or Dankort card on mobile phone, please
be aware of the maximum limit per transaction without PIN-code
authorisation. You will always be able to find the effective maximum
amount on &BANKNAVN. homepage. &BANKNAVN. is entitled to change the
amount. Adjustments will not be notified in advance unless the amount is
increased or decreased by more than 50 per cent.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In case the purchase exceeds the effective payment limit, you will
automatically be asked to confirm the payment by entering the PIN
code. At intervals, you may be asked to enter the PIN code, even
though the amount is within the effective payment limit.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Gaming and lottery
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Using your Dankort card with businesses, mainly offering gaming and
betting solutions, including casinos, lottery ticket providers, racing
tracks, etc., a maximum limit for every 24 hours may be specified. The
maximum will appear from the pricelist of the bank in question.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Withdrawal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A maximum daily withdrawal limit applies to your Dankort card. This
sum is stated on the &BANKNAVN. price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In addition, individual businesses can set limits for use of the card.
.sp 3mm
Moreover, your bank may have set a limit on the size of the sums you
may withdraw. You may be charged a fee every time you make a cash
withdrawal - irrespective of the sum you withdraw.
&BANKNAVN. price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.2¤Purchases in shops
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can use your Dankort card to pay for goods and services in shops
that accept Dankort.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The business or website will display a sign to indicate that it accepts
Dankort cards as a form of payment.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can use your card to make purchases over the Internet and for
mail order and telephone order purchases. You can also use your Dankort
card to make payments in self-service machines.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you have an account owing in your favour from a shop, the shop can
use your Dankort card to deposit the money on your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You may not use your Dankort card for unlawful purposes, including the
purchase of goods or services that are illegal according to local
legislation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.3¤Withdrawal of sums from your account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In principle, purchases and cash withdrawals will be debited from your
account on the same day that you make the purchase or withdrawal. The
time of debiting from your account will, however, depend on when
&BANKNAVN. receives the transaction.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
