2.5 Loyalty programmes
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can connect your Dankort card to loyalty programmes, e.g. with the
purpose of earning personal bonus/discount or for charitable/supporting
purposes. You can see the approved loyalty programmes here
.us http://dankort.dk/Pages/Loyalitetskort.aspx
